GENERAL INSTALLATION INFORMATION



=Requirements=

Make sure you have your PHP interpreter built with the following modules before you proceed with the installation:

1. Sockets
2. Sessions
3. mysql


=Installation=

Copy all files to the document root of your vhost and point your browser to the index without. Example: http://www.openwow.com/. Installation process will being instantly. 
You will be guided through a a number of self-explanatory steps to finish the installation. Make sure you satisfy all what is required during the process. After the installation script is finished
you will be forwarded to your fresh main page where you can start your customizations.




